<h1 align="center">🛡️ Scam RAG Detector</h1>

<p align="center">
AI-powered scam detection assistant using <b>Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG)</b>.
<br>
Paste any suspicious message and get an instant risk analysis.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>🚀 Demo</h2>

<p><b>Input Message</b></p>

<pre>
Congratulations! You've won a $1000 gift card.
Click here to claim before it expires!
</pre>

<p><b>Output</b></p>

<pre>
Is this a scam? YES
Risk Level: HIGH
Reason: Uses urgency tactics and unrealistic rewards — common phishing pattern.
</pre>

<hr>

<h2>🧠 How It Works</h2>

<pre>
spam.txt  →  ingest.py  →  FAISS vector DB
                               ↓
user message → similarity search → LLM (Groq) → risk analysis
</pre>

<ol>
<li><b>Ingest</b> – Loads spam messages and converts them into embeddings</li>
<li><b>Store</b> – Saves embeddings in a FAISS vector database</li>
<li><b>Retrieve</b> – Finds similar scam patterns</li>
<li><b>Analyze</b> – LLM explains whether the message is a scam</li>
</ol>

<hr>

<h2>📁 Project Structure</h2>

<pre>
Scam RAG/
│
├── app.py            # Streamlit UI
├── rag.py            # Retrieval + LLM logic
├── ingest.py         # Build vector database
├── spam.txt          # Spam dataset
├── vector_db/        # FAISS index (generated)
├── requirements.txt
├── .env
└── .gitignore
</pre>

<hr>

<h2>⚙️ Setup</h2>

<h3>1. Clone Repository</h3>

<pre>
git clone https://github.com/ShazaMumtaz20/scam-rag-detector.git
cd scam-rag-detector
</pre>

<h3>2. Create Virtual Environment</h3>

<pre>
python -m venv venv
</pre>

<h3>Activate (Windows)</h3>

<pre>
venv\Scripts\activate
</pre>

<h3>3. Install Dependencies</h3>

<pre>
pip install -r requirements.txt
</pre>

<hr>

<h2>🔑 Add Groq API Key</h2>

<p>Get a free key from:</p>

<p>
<a href="https://console.groq.com">https://console.groq.com</a>
</p>

<p>Create a <b>.env</b> file:</p>

<pre>
GROQ_API_KEY=your-key-here
</pre>

<p>Or set it manually:</p>

<pre>
# Windows
$env:GROQ_API_KEY="your-key-here"

# Mac/Linux
export GROQ_API_KEY="your-key-here"
</pre>

<hr>

<h2>📦 Build Vector Database</h2>

<pre>
python ingest.py
</pre>

<hr>

<h2>▶ Run the Application</h2>

<pre>
streamlit run app.py
</pre>

<p>Open in browser:</p>

<pre>
http://localhost:8501
</pre>

<hr>

<h2>🧰 Tech Stack</h2>

<table>
<tr>
<th>Tool</th>
<th>Purpose</th>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Streamlit</td>
<td>Web Interface</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>FAISS</td>
<td>Vector Similarity Search</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>LangChain</td>
<td>RAG Pipeline</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>HuggingFace</td>
<td>Embeddings (all-MiniLM-L6-v2)</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Groq</td>
<td>LLM Inference</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>Sentence Transformers</td>
<td>Text Embeddings</td>
</tr>

</table>

<hr>

<h2>📄 Dataset Format</h2>

<p><b>spam.txt</b> must be tab separated:</p>

<pre>
ham	Hey, are you free tomorrow?
spam	You have been selected for a FREE iPhone. Claim now!
</pre>

<p>Only <b>spam</b> rows are indexed into the vector database.</p>

<hr>

<h2>⚠️ Notes</h2>

<ul>
<li><b>.env</b> and <b>vector_db</b> are excluded from GitHub</li>
<li>Run <b>ingest.py</b> locally to regenerate the database</li>
<li>Groq free tier may have rate limits</li>
<li>Embeddings run locally</li>
</ul>

